        <div class="loop-img-container">
            <section>
                <h2>Lords of War</h2>
                <p>In the vast lore of Warcraft, the Warrior stands as a formidable symbol of strength and valor,
                    embodying
                    the essence of battle and honor. Honed through relentless training and unwavering determination,
                    Warriors are skilled combatants, adept in wielding various weapons and donning heavy armor. Whether
                    leading the charge into battle or defending their homeland, Warriors inspire allies with their
                    courage
                    and strike fear into the hearts of their foes. Driven by duty and loyalty, they confront any threat
                    with
                    unyielding resolve, standing as guardians of peace and defenders of justice. Even in times of peace,
                    the
                    Warrior's spirit remains unbroken, ever-ready to face any challenge that may arise, ensuring the
                    protection of their kin and the preservation of righteousness.</p>

                <h2>Class information</h2>
                <p>
                    Warriors in Warcraft are versatile combatants, excelling in both offense and defense on the
                    battlefield.
                    Clad in heavy plate armor and wielding a variety of weapons, from swords and axes to maces and
                    polearms,
                    Warriors are masters of martial prowess. They can adopt different specializations to suit their
                    preferred combat style: Arms Warriors focus on dealing devastating blows with two-handed weapons,
                    Fury
                    Warriors unleash a flurry of attacks with dual-wielding weapons, and Protection Warriors specialize
                    in
                    tanking, drawing enemy attention and mitigating damage to protect their allies. With a wide range of
                    abilities, including powerful strikes, defensive maneuvers, and crowd control techniques, Warriors
                    are
                    indispensable assets in any battle, capable of turning the tide of war with their unmatched skill
                    and
                    resilience.</p>
            </section>

            <figure>
                <img id="img1" src="sprites/warrior1.png" alt="Orc Warrior">
