        <div class="abilities-container">
            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/berserkerstance.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3> Berserzer Stance</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p> An aggressive stance. Critical hit chance is increased by 3% and all damage taken is increased
                        by 10%. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/execute.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3> Execute </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p> Attempts to finish off a foe, causing up to [2.0 * (107.415% of Attack power)] Physical damage
                        based on Rage spent. Only usable on enemies that have less than 20% health. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/battleshout.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3> Battle Shout</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p>
                        Increases the attack power of all raid and party members within 100 yards by 5% for 1 hour..
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/rend.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3>Rend</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p> Wounds the target, causing (73.83% of Attack power) Physical damage instantly and an additional
                        (112.875% of Attack power) Bleed damage over 15 sec. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/sunderarmor.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3>Sunder Armor</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p> Sunders the target's armor, reducing it by 450 per Sunder Armor and causes a high amount of
                        threat. Can be applied up to 5 times. Lasts 30 sec. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/berserkerrage.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3> Berserzer Rage</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p> The warrior enters a berserker rage, becoming immune to Fear and Incapacitate effects and
                        generating extra rage when taking damage. Lasts 10 sec. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/charge.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3>Charge</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p> Charge to an enemy, dealing (21% of Attack power) Physical damage, rooting it for 1 sec </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ability">
                <div class="ability-header">
                    <img src="sprites/shieldblock.png" alt="Icon">
                    <h3> Shield Block</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="ability-desc">
                    <p> Raise your shield, blocking all melee attacks against you for 6 sec. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

